'''沙希德阿巴斯普尔大坝''' ({{lang-fa|سد شهید عباسپور}}) ，又称'''卡伦河一号大坝'''，位于[[伊朗|伊朗]][[胡齊斯坦省|胡齐斯坦省]][[馬斯吉德蘇萊曼|马斯吉德苏莱曼]]城东北50公里处的[[卡伦河_(伊朗)|卡伦河]]上。该坝属于拱坝，一期工程于1969年开工，1976年建成<ref>[https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=de&u=http://de.academic.ru/dic.nsf/dewiki/752587&ei=tZA6TIKhEoL78AaEqfinBg&sa=X&oi=translate&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CDgQ7gEwCDgK&prev=/search%3Fq%3D%2522Karun%2B1%2522%2BDam%26start%3D10%26hl%3Den%26client%3Dfirefox-a%26sa%3DN%26rls%3Dorg.mozilla:en-US:official Shahid Abbaspour dam] {{Wayback|url=https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=de&u=http%3A%2F%2Fde.academic.ru%2Fdic.nsf%2Fdewiki%2F752587&ei=tZA6TIKhEoL78AaEqfinBg&sa=X&oi=translate&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CDgQ7gEwCDgK&prev=%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2522Karun%2B1%2522%2BDam%26start%3D10%26hl%3Den%26client%3Dfirefox-a%26sa%3DN%26rls%3Dorg.mozilla%3Aen-US%3Aofficial |date=20150928042926 }}'', translation from German.</ref>。最初命名为'''礼萨汗大坝'''，[[伊朗伊斯蘭革命|伊朗伊斯兰革命]]后改为现名<ref>Peter Beaumont, ''[http://www.jstor.org/stable/1796535 Water Resource Development in Iran] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jstor.org/stable/1796535 |date=20160303165407 }}'', in [[The_Geographical_Journal|The Geographical Journal]], Vol. 140, No. 3 (Oct., 1974), pp. 418-431</ref>。它是卡伦河上一系列水利水电工程计划中的第一座大坝<ref>P.T. Shourijed, A Soroush, N. Nemati, A.H Izad-doustdar, ''[https://books.google.com/books?id=6XzSYK9vNXQC&pg=PA290&lpg=PA290&dq=%22Karun+1%22+Dam&source=bl&ots=piAcWm-THF&sig=HtUHKo7UZtebj1CQ_CvbGyh5wLY&hl=en&ei=HYo6TMGiLoL68Aa85cSnBg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CDkQ6AEwCA#v=snippet&q=%22Karun%20I%22&f=false Karun River hydropower cascade development and its socio- environmental impacts]'' in L. Berga, et al. (eds), Dams and Reservoirs, Societies and Environment in the 21st Century ..., Volume 1, (2006)</ref>。

== 结构 ==
该坝采用混凝土双曲拱坝，坝高200米，坝顶宽6米<ref name="MOE">[http://news.moe.org.ir/vgld.90o2yt0zshf62yyal..html Iran Ministry of Energy News] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081226230242/http://news.moe.org.ir/vgld.90o2yt0zshf62yyal..html |date=2008-12-26 }}</ref>，大坝被设计在卡伦河上一个狭窄的岩石峡谷中，通过双曲拱的设计，能够将上游储水水流所带来的压力，借助坝体的弧面向外部传导至大坝两侧的峡谷山体，有助于进一步增强大坝的抗水压能力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/buildingbig/dam/basics.html|title=Dam basics|publisher=|accessdate=2008-06-11|archive-date=2007-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071203113123/http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/buildingbig/dam/basics.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 发电 ==
大坝有两座发电站房，分别建成于1976年和1995年，每个发电站方包含四个{{convert|2000|MW}}[[水輪發電機|水轮机发电机组]]，大坝总发电能力达到{{convert|2000|MW}}。大坝发电网络与[[輸電網路|公共电网]]相连接，大部分的发电用于尖峰时刻的用电需求。

